it:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/ad24196645ebfd6ff1c4dbe50c586b49/f2d49/Image-1.17.20-CES.png 300w,\n/static/ad24196645ebfd6ff1c4dbe50c586b49/ff59c/Image-1.17.20-CES.png 600w,\n/static/ad24196645ebfd6ff1c4dbe50c586b49/5ece7/Image-1.17.20-CES.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" srcSet=\"/static/ad24196645ebfd6ff1c4dbe50c586b49/f2d49/Image-1.17.20-CES.png 300w,\n/static/ad24196645ebfd6ff1c4dbe50c586b49/ff59c/Image-1.17.20-CES.png 600w,\n/static/ad24196645ebfd6ff1c4dbe50c586b49/5ece7/Image-1.17.20-CES.png 1200w\" src=\"/static/ad24196645ebfd6ff1c4dbe50c586b49/5ece7/Image-1.17.20-CES.png\" alt=\"dnanudge display at the 2019 Consumer Electronics Show\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/ad24196645ebfd6ff1c4dbe50c586b49/f2d49/Image-1.17.20-CES.png 300w,\n/static/ad24196645ebfd6ff1c4dbe50c586b49/ff59c/Image-1.17.20-CES.png 600w,\n/static/ad24196645ebfd6ff1c4dbe50c586b49/5ece7/Image-1.17.20-CES.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" srcset=\"/static/ad24196645ebfd6ff1c4dbe50c586b49/f2d49/Image-1.17.20-CES.png 300w,\n/static/ad24196645ebfd6ff1c4dbe50c586b49/ff59c/Image-1.17.20-CES.png 600w,\n/static/ad24196645ebfd6ff1c4dbe50c586b49/5ece7/Image-1.17.20-CES.png 1200w\" src=\"/static/ad24196645ebfd6ff1c4dbe50c586b49/5ece7/Image-1.17.20-CES.png\" alt=\"dnanudge display at the 2019 Consumer Electronics Show\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></p>\n<p>Some of our agency team members traveled to Las Vegas last week to attend the 2020 Consumer Electronics Show. The PM Group is always staying on the cutting edge of what is possible in the world of marketing and advertising by studying emerging trends, technology, and consumer interests.</p>\n<p><span class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5093 size-full inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:960px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:75%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/64d85a2675f80412a54403284869d4bf/46946/IMG_20200114_090707_01.jpg 240w,\n/static/64d85a2675f80412a54403284869d4bf/55489/IMG_20200114_090707_01.jpg 480w,\n/static/64d85a2675f80412a54403284869d4bf/18e3b/IMG_20200114_090707_01.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" srcSet=\"/static/64d85a2675f80412a54403284869d4bf/46946/IMG_20200114_090707_01.jpg 240w,\n/static/64d85a2675f80412a54403284869d4bf/55489/IMG_20200114_090707_01.jpg 480w,\n/static/64d85a2675f80412a54403284869d4bf/18e3b/IMG_20200114_090707_01.jpg 960w\" src=\"/static/64d85a2675f80412a54403284869d4bf/18e3b/IMG_20200114_090707_01.jpg\" alt=\"Ford Mustang display at the 2019 Consumer Electronics Show\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/64d85a2675f80412a54403284869d4bf/46946/IMG_20200114_090707_01.jpg 240w,\n/static/64d85a2675f80412a54403284869d4bf/55489/IMG_20200114_090707_01.jpg 480w,\n/static/64d85a2675f80412a54403284869d4bf/18e3b/IMG_20200114_090707_01.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" srcset=\"/static/64d85a2675f80412a54403284869d4bf/46946/IMG_20200114_090707_01.jpg 240w,\n/static/64d85a2675f80412a54403284869d4bf/55489/IMG_20200114_090707_01.jpg 480w,\n/static/64d85a2675f80412a54403284869d4bf/18e3b/IMG_20200114_090707_01.jpg 960w\" src=\"/static/64d85a2675f80412a54403284869d4bf/18e3b/IMG_20200114_090707_01.jpg\" alt=\"Ford Mustang display at the 2019 Consumer Electronics Show\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5094 size-full inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:719px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:75%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/a154b2e4b9f7ca8c05256d906f418a09/388fb/IMG_20200114_090649_01b.jpg 180w,\n/static/a154b2e4b9f7ca8c05256d906f418a09/1ff7f/IMG_20200114_090649_01b.jpg 360w,\n/static/a154b2e4b9f7ca8c05256d906f418a09/798c1/IMG_20200114_090649_01b.jpg 719w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 719px) 100vw, 719px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 719px) 100vw, 719px\" srcSet=\"/static/a154b2e4b9f7ca8c05256d906f418a09/388fb/IMG_20200114_090649_01b.jpg 180w,\n/static/a154b2e4b9f7ca8c05256d906f418a09/1ff7f/IMG_20200114_090649_01b.jpg 360w,\n/static/a154b2e4b9f7ca8c05256d906f418a09/798c1/IMG_20200114_090649_01b.jpg 719w\" src=\"/static/a154b2e4b9f7ca8c05256d906f418a09/798c1/IMG_20200114_090649_01b.jpg\" alt=\"AT&amp;amp;T display at the 2019 Consumer Electronics Show\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/a154b2e4b9f7ca8c05256d906f418a09/388fb/IMG_20200114_090649_01b.jpg 180w,\n/static/a154b2e4b9f7ca8c05256d906f418a09/1ff7f/IMG_20200114_090649_01b.jpg 360w,\n/static/a154b2e4b9f7ca8c05256d906f418a09/798c1/IMG_20200114_090649_01b.jpg 719w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 719px) 100vw, 719px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 719px) 100vw, 719px\" srcset=\"/static/a154b2e4b9f7ca8c05256d906f418a09/388fb/IMG_20200114_090649_01b.jpg 180w,\n/static/a154b2e4b9f7ca8c05256d906f418a09/1ff7f/IMG_20200114_090649_01b.jpg 360w,\n/static/a154b2e4b9f7ca8c05256d906f418a09/798c1/IMG_20200114_090649_01b.jpg 719w\" src=\"/static/a154b2e4b9f7ca8c05256d906f418a09/798c1/IMG_20200114_090649_01b.jpg\" alt=\"AT&amp;T display at the 2019 Consumer Electronics Show\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></p>\n<p>With over 4,500 exhibitors, the team stayed busy making connections with top of the line, innovative tech companies to keep expanding who we can serve and what we can provide to our clients in the years to come. Ever changing consumer expectations, behaviors, and beliefs are often directly impacted by technology. What was once “possible” becomes “every day”. Understanding what’s coming in the next 10 years for our clients is important to an agency; so, we stay ahead of imminent changes to how people interact, shop, solve problems, and live their daily lives. If your brand needs a peek into the immediate consumer future, contact The PM Group so we can collaborate to create a strategy that works best for your brand.</p>\n<p><span class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5095 size-full inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:960px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:75%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover