7d47691a446929/38ece/IMG_20200114_090702_01.jpg\" alt=\"Arcade 1Up pop up at the 2019 Consumer Electronics Show\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>About The PM Group</strong></a>: The PM Group was founded in 1988. For over 31 years, the agency has continued to grow and is San Antonio’s largest advertising agency. The PM Group’s client roster spans numerous industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profit, real estate and fitness. In addition, the agency hosts an annual Charity Gala that to date has raised millions of dollars for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations in the last 15 years! In the past 10 years, The PM Group has raised both directly and indirectly over $12 million for these charities. It is our way of giving back to the community that we so humbly serve.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\n","title":"The PM Group Stays on the Cutting Edge at Consumer Electronics Show","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"The PM Group Stays on the Cutting Edge at Consumer Electronics Show","url":"/the-pm-group-consumer-electronics-show/"}],"title":"The PM Group Attends the Consumer Electronics Show","metaDesc":"The team stayed busy making connections with innovative tech companies to keep expanding who we can serve and what we can provide to our clients...","focuskw":"Consumer Electronics Show","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"The PM Group Attends the Consumer Electronics Show","opengraphDescription":"The team stayed busy making connections with innovative tech companies to keep expanding who we can serve and what we can provide to our clients...","opengraphImage":{"altText":"dnanudge display at the 2019 Consumer Electron